[Major Porter] That's
why I love you, major.


16
00:02:08.572 --> 00:02:09.448
Five clicks north,

17
00:02:09.532 --> 00:02:11.283
we should find a second
division hospital.


18
00:02:11.534 --> 00:02:14.411
Heads up, they hydrated.
We ain't in London no more.


19
00:02:14.578 --> 00:02:16.372
We got trees here,
so watch your six.


20
00:02:16.872 --> 00:02:18.124
- Copy that.
- Yes, Sir.


21
00:02:18.207 --> 00:02:19.625
No more tea time, huh, Major?

22
00:02:19.708 --> 00:02:21.544
No more tea time, Private.

23
00:02:21.627 --> 00:02:25.047
Just remember this is
a quick sweep.


24
00:02:25.131 --> 00:02:26.006
Five, six days,

25
00:02:26.090 --> 00:02:28.425
You could be home having
grits with grandma, girls.


26
