Oh, my granny makes
the best grits in all of Texas.


27
00:02:31.303 --> 00:02:32.513
Well, you go ahead and tell Nana

28
00:02:32.596 --> 00:02:34.140
she got a new grandson
named Gustavo,


29
00:02:34.223 --> 00:02:35.266
and I want some of them grits.

30
00:02:35.349 --> 00:02:37.101
I wouldn't care much for
your grandma's grits,


31
00:02:37.184 --> 00:02:38.644
but I'd love to meet
your sister.


32
00:02:38.769 --> 00:02:41.730
Hey, sonny boy, you too
young for that,


33
00:02:41.814 --> 00:02:44.233
but maybe when you're older,
young gun.


34
00:02:46.402 --> 00:02:50.448
[distant gunfire and explosions]

35
00:02:52.825 --> 00:02:55.828
[suspenseful music]

36
00:03:45.252 --> 00:03:46.587
[rustling noise]

37
00:03:59.892 --> 00:04:01.977
Take cover! Watch your six!

38
00:04:02.436 --> 00:04:04.271
[gunfire]

39
00:04:10.903 --> 00:04:13.155
[men yelling]

40
00:04:27.211 --> 00:04:28.254
[gun clicks]

41
00:04:28.337 --> 00:04:29.296
I'm out!

42
00:04:48.274 --> 00:04:49.191
[gun fires]

43
00:05:11.505 --> 00:05:13.340
You're a cold-blooded killer,
Sir.


44
00:05:13.424 --> 00:05:16.719
Let me look. You've been
long-bladed, soldier.


45
00:05:17.136 --> 00:05:18.262
Keep some pressure on that,
okay?


46
00:05:18.345 --> 00:05:20.097
- All right, okay.
- Pressure.


47
00:05:20.222 --> 00:05:21.724
All right. Let's see
what I've got.


48
00:05:21.807 --> 00:05:25.644
Hey, you make sure you call
my mom. She's gonna be mad.


49
00:05:26.771 --> 00:05:28.189
She's gonna be real mad.

50
00:05:30.107 --> 00:05:31.942
Private Shaw, listen to me.

51
00:05:32.026 --> 00:05:33.527
- Yes.
- We gotta move, gotta go quietly.


52
00:05:33.611 --> 00:05:34.653
- Can you make it?
- Yes, sir.


53
00:05:34.737 --> 00:05:35.821
Up we go. On your feet.

54
00:05:35.905 --> 00:05:37.114
[Shaw groaning]

55
00:05:37.573 --> 00:05:39.575
[dramatic music]

56
00:05:39.742 --> 00:05:41.243
[percussive hit]

57
00:05:47.625 --> 00:05:50.544
[birds chirping]

58
00:05:54.006 --> 00:05:56.967
[distant rumbling]

59
00:06:34.588 --> 00:06:35.631
[Vic sighing]

60
00:07:03.367 --> 00:07:04.243
[Vic sighing]

61
00:07:08.664 --> 00:07:10.833
[Timepiece chain rattling]

62
00:07:13.043 --> 00:07:14.211
[Dog tag chain rattling]

63
00:07:14.336 --> 00:07:17.173
[rhythmic hitting]

64
00:07:32.271 --> 00:07:35.232
