263
00:19:53.137 --> 00:19:54.638
That old tofah?

264
00:19:54.763 --> 00:19:56.474
Yep. Makes sense.

265
00:19:57.641 --> 00:19:59.518
No wonder these stitches hurt.

266
00:19:59.810 --> 00:20:01.145
