Hope you didn't use
that hand on me.


268
00:20:09.361 --> 00:20:11.322
- I got it under control.
- How's that?


269
00:20:12.740 --> 00:20:14.241
I use a heavy bag.

270
00:20:14.366 --> 00:20:16.869
