291
00:21:33.904 --> 00:21:35.739
I say that's the whole
goddamn point.


292
00:21:37.533 --> 00:21:38.576
Cheers to that.

293
00:21:42.037 --> 00:21:43.664
What can I do for you, Major?

294
00:21:45.416 --> 00:21:49.128
Well, I wanted to meet
the legend and to warn you, sir.


295
00:21:50.754 --> 00:21:51.714
Warn me?

296
00:21:53.090 --> 00:21:54.842
Me and my men were doing
a sweep down the hill


297
00:21:54.967 --> 00:21:57.761
and we were ambushed.
Most of us were wiped out


298
00:21:57.845 --> 00:22:00.639
besides myself and the Private
who almost bled to death.


299
00:22:02.558 --> 00:22:04.643
I lay low for a couple hours,
but I overheard one of them


300
00:22:04.810 --> 00:22:06.729
