302
00:22:09.398 --> 00:22:11.859
A real nasty son of a bitch,
in case you never heard of him.


303
00:22:11.942 --> 00:22:12.943
I know he is.

304
00:22:15.237 --> 00:22:17.114
When's this attack
supposed to happen?


305
