what happens out here.


312
00:22:47.144 --> 00:22:48.813
Well then, I'd say
ready your men.


313
00:22:48.938 --> 00:22:50.314
Take a look around, Major.

314
00:22:51.398 --> 00:22:53.651
We got a few dozen wounded
GIs and half of them


315
