318
00:23:03.869 --> 00:23:05.162
Anything else, Major?

319
00:23:07.706 --> 00:23:09.208
We're sharing a toast here, sir.

320
00:23:09.291 --> 00:23:12.211
But we have a situation and
this is what you're gonna do


321
