"Thank you."


418
00:29:06.774 --> 00:29:10.194
Okay. I will.

419
00:29:12.279 --> 00:29:13.197
I will.

420
00:29:17.576 --> 00:29:20.704
[distant explosions]

421
00:29:23.582 --> 00:29:25.876
[sad music]

422
00:29:49.775 --> 00:29:51.235
You know you don't have
to hide that from me.


423
00:29:51.735 --> 00:29:52.862
Yeah, yeah, I know.

424
00:29:55.281 --> 00:29:57.241
The Major's a real asshole,
isn't he?


425
00:29:58.909 --> 00:30:00.286
It's how they manufacture 'em.

426
00:30:01.203 --> 00:30:02.955
Maybe we should order a factory

427
00:30:04.373 --> 00:30:06.792
Fortunately, these bastards
tend to get results.


