I'm gonna get you home, soldier.


467
00:32:52.666 --> 00:32:53.834
I'm gonna get you home.

468
00:32:59.173 --> 00:33:01.759
[anxious music]

469
00:33:14.522 --> 00:33:16.148
[man coughing]

470
00:33:25.783 --> 00:33:27.785
[gunshots firing]

471
00:33:43.384 --> 00:33:46.679
[indistinct chatter]

472
00:34:06.574 --> 00:34:08.659
I figured I'd find you two
out here without weapons.


473
00:34:10.326 --> 00:34:11.328
We don't get issued guns.

474
00:34:11.412 --> 00:34:12.872
Don't gimme that shit.

475
00:34:13.956 --> 00:34:16.625
