504
00:40:04.932 --> 00:40:06.350
It's good to have him back.

505
00:40:08.436 --> 00:40:09.562
So, what next?

506
00:40:11.564 --> 00:40:13.607
We radio for help
and get the hell outta here.


507
00:40:14.442 --> 00:40:16.610
That's a negative. Not possible.

508
00:40:17.111 --> 00:40:19.238
- Why not?
