Whatever you can carry.

549
00:42:52.516 --> 00:42:55.186
Well, there it is.

550
00:42:55.895 --> 00:42:59.023
- There's what?
- Stress reliever, right?


551
00:43:00.191 --> 00:43:02.735
By the way, wonderful job
being off the mainland.


552
00:43:03.444 --> 00:43:05.488
That's a potato sack
I found in the jungle.


553
00:43:06.530 --> 00:43:08.574
- Filled it with sand, right?
- Yeah.


554
00:43:08.657 --> 00:43:09.784
Yeah, well, I'll tell you what.

555
00:43:09.867 --> 00:43:11.076
Maybe you can help me fix that

556
00:43:11.160 --> 00:43:12.953
and hang it back up
before we leave,


557
00:43:13.370 --> 00:43:14.747
maybe I'll take a few swings.

558
00:43:14.830 --> 00:43:16.457
Well, I think you're gonna
have plenty opportunity


559
00:43:16.540 --> 00:43:18.375
to hit other things
other than a potato sack.


560
00:43:19.710 --> 00:43:22.004
This works. Let's get
'em down here.


561
00:43:46.779 --> 00:43:48.155
[percussive hit]

562
00:44:04.255 --> 00:44:05.756
[machine gun fire]

563
00:44:05.923 --> 00:44:10.136
[men shouting
and women screaming]


564
00:44:24.233 --> 00:44:26.569
Move, move, move! Move!
Let's go!


565
00:44:30.865 --> 00:44:31.782
He's hit!

566
