Stay with me. Stay with me.

567
00:44:45.796 --> 00:44:46.797
Here you go.

568
00:44:48.591 --> 00:44:50.092
[explosion]

569
00:44:50.676 --> 00:44:51.927
- Cover me.
- Go, go, go, go!


570
00:44:52.011 --> 00:44:54.847
[rapid gunfire]

571
00:45:01.479 --> 00:45:03.230
[Vic screaming]

572
00:45:05.441 --> 00:45:07.651
[rapid gunfire continues]

573
00:45:14.408 --> 00:45:17.578
[anxious music ends]

574
00:45:22.166 --> 00:45:23.083
He's gone.

575
00:45:23.876 --> 00:45:26.003
Morphine! I need some
morphine here!


576
00:45:26.128 --> 00:45:27.463
- I'm coming!
- You're wasting your time.


577
00:45:27.838 --> 00:45:30.716
- Shut up.
- Stay with me. Come on, man.


578
00:45:30.841 --> 00:45:31.884
Stay with me.

579
00:45:36.472 --> 00:45:38.557
